description: Application for variation of condition no. 1 (consented plans)  planning permission dated 13/01/2017, ref: PA/16/00139 (as amendment to ref: PA/12/00315) which gave consent for the erection of two buildings of 55 and 50 storeys to provide 764 residential units (Use Class C3) and ancillary uses, plus 850 sqm. ground floor retail uses (Use Classes A1 -A4), provision of ancillary amenity space, landscaping, public dockside walkway and pedestrian route, basement parking, servicing and a new vehicular access.Changes to building heights, consented tower facade, sky garden and pool and dockside changes.     Amendments proposed:  Minor façade changes to East Tower Podium East Elevation  Minor façade changes to East Tower East Elevation L03 Winter garden Removal of mid level plant rooms and amended BMU parking strategy Minor increase in height of Lift Over Run and Building Heights Increase in residential units from 764 to 767  Changes to two of the penthouse units from 2 bed to 3 bed  Addition
